        "text": "XML -&gt; JSON\nXML Schema -&gt; JSON-schema\nWSDL -&gt; Swager\nSOAP -&gt; JSON-RPC\n\nIs there really that much difference between \"XML world\" and \"JSON world\" now? :joy:\nThe real difference is XML stuff was actually standardised while JSON stuff is ad-hoc, slightly incompatible and almost everybody does it in their own special way.\n\nNot mentioning JSON still lacks _comments_! :rolling_on_the_floor_laughing:",
